stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NEW : Client submits container spec
    NEW --> LOCALIZING : Local resources (configs, files) download
    LOCALIZING --> LOCALIZED : Resources ready
    LOCALIZED --> LAUNCHING : NodeManager runs LinuxContainerExecutor
    LAUNCHING --> IMAGE_PULL : Docker daemon pulls container image (if missing)
    IMAGE_PULL --> CONTAINER_RUNNING : Docker starts task process
    CONTAINER_RUNNING --> CRITICAL_OUT_OF_MEMORY : Exceeds hardware memory limits
    CONTAINER_RUNNING --> SUCCESSFULLY_FINISHED : Process exits code 0
    CONTAINER_RUNNING --> CONTAINER_FAILED : Process crashes (non-zero code)
    CRITICAL_OUT_OF_MEMORY --> CLEANING_UP : NodeManager terminates container
    CONTAINER_FAILED --> CLEANING_UP
    SUCCESSFULLY_FINISHED --> CLEANING_UP
    CLEANING_UP --> [*] : Log aggregation & release resources
